bargain for or anticipate. We discussed this issue, along with the end=20
user margin issue, with various stakeholders at a joint SEC-CFTC=20
roundtable in December, and are taking the input we received at the=20
roundtable and from other sources into account in writing proposed=20
rules.
Conclusion
    The Dodd-Frank Act provides the SEC with important tools to better=20
meet the challenges of today's financial marketplace and fulfill our=20
mission to protect investors, maintain fair, orderly, and efficient=20
markets, promote the prompt and accurate clearance and settlement of=20
securities transactions, and facilitate capital formation. As we=20
proceed with implementation, we look forward to continuing to work=20
closely with Congress, our fellow regulators, and members of the=20
financial and investing public. Thank you for inviting me to share with=20
you our progress on and plans for implementation. I look forward to=20
answering your questions.
