concentrate risk and thus have the potential to transmit shocks=20
throughout the financial markets. The Financial Stability Oversight=20
Council is responsible for designating utilities as systemically=20
important. Through its role on the council, the Board helped develop=20
the designation process that was released for comment in March.=20
