needs resulting from their derivatives portfolios.
    Our proposal for margin imposes initial and variation margin=20
requirements on the noncleared swaps held by swap dealers or major swap=20
participants that have a prudential regulator. For swaps with a=20
nonfinancial end user counterparty, the proposed rule would not specify=20
