monitored as part of the credit approval process, below which the end=20
user would not have to post margin. For swaps with other=20
counterparties, the proposal would cap the allowable threshold for=20
unsecured credit exposure on noncleared swaps. In addition, the=20
proposal would only apply a margin requirement to contracts entered=20
