                                       U.S. Senate,
          Committee on Banking, Housing, and Urban Affairs,
                                                    Washington, DC.
    The Committee met at 2:45 p.m., in room SD-538, Dirksen=20
Senate Office Building, Hon. Tim Johnson, Chairman of the=20
