    The implementation of these titles is a substantial undertaking and=20
raises a number of challenges. Accordingly, we have been engaging in an=20
open and transparent implementation process, seeking input on the=20
various rulemakings from interested parties even before issuing formal=20
rule proposals. We will continue to seek input on each proposal with=20
the goal of producing effective and workable regulation of derivatives=20
activities and oversight of financial market utilities designated as=20
systemically important and financial institutions that engage in=20
payment, clearing, and settlement activities designated as systemically=20
