management standards that would apply to those designated utilities=20
supervised by the Board under title VIII. \1\ As part of title VIII,=20
the Board was given new authority to provide designated utilities with=20
access to Reserve Bank accounts, payment services, and emergency=20
collateralized liquidity in unusual and exigent circumstances. We are=20
carefully considering ways to implement this authority in a manner that=20
protects taxpayers and limits any rise in moral hazard.
