client protection models would be most appropriate for customers=20
clearing swaps. \14\ As LCH.Clearnet stated in its response to the=20
ANPR, \15\ we believe that customers should above all be able to=20
preserve the collateral protections they are offered in the bilateral=20
uncleared swaps environment.
